{"tid":1474493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"817光復紅土反對通知書已出，係香港人就唔該繼續去","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T05:21:47.000Z","uid":13572,"like":54,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6c875f62e218c14c0fe6110ed1394ba482afecd7","tid":1474493,"uid":13572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地啊同我講留力？之前元朗我地都無話留力而無去啦<br />\n紅土唔係香港一部份啊？大陸人侵佔香港唔係其中一個社會問題啊？<br />\n五大訴求重要 光復靜土一樣重要<br />\n唔好同我講話唔夠人所以要取消 唔夠人係因為你地一個二個仆街唔撚黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">818要去</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">817更加要去！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"df5e9b1720a79d453ee1dcf81d8e3496b2fad8d6","tid":1474493,"uid":13572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b15623a6557b4857a03f7ccd2f76c9f7fb61ff0","tid":1474493,"uid":13572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18ea9b868b6cf1404c779aab8d44115e0d09df3a","tid":1474493,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http